author_ssm: Matt Moore, 2003, Jenny Pachuki and Shelley Lightburn, 2006.
abstract_ssm: Cecily Brownstone was the Associated Press food editor for nearly forty years, as well as the author of Cecily Brownstone's Associated Press Cookbook (Associated Press, 1972). Brownstone amassed a comprehensive collection of materials relating to American cookery, including cookbooks, pamphlets, postcards, menus, recipe boxes, and more.
